### v0.2.0

- Instead of using template rewrite, use js dynamic repairing method.
- Add DjangoCheckboxNormalizeAdmin to normalize one site.
- Add `DJANGO_CHECKBOX_NORMALIZE_FOR_ALL = True` to normalize for all modeladmins.

